Kansas v. Missouri. May 27, 1940.

The motion for leave to file a bill of complaint is granted *615and process is ordered to issue returnable September 1, next.

Messrs. Jay S. Parker, Attorney General of Kansas, A. B. Mitchell, Assistant Attorney General, Clarence V. Beck, and Errett P. Scrivner for complainant.
